  "title": "경복궁 야간개장",
  "addDate": "2013. 5. 24.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110168723081",
  "html_size": 189426,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110168723081\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110168723081\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&#65279;23일 밤에 경복궁을 가기로 합니다.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">미리 인터넷 사전 예매를 하고 광화문으로 향합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">시청앞부터 차가 막히는걸 보고선 '아 사람이 많겠구나' 싶었죠.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">광화문에 내려보니 사람이 정말 많더군요</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">광화문 성문이 열려서 거기로 들어가는데, 내 의지로 걷는게 아니라 떠밀려 들어갑니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">애들 챙기느라 진땀 흘렸네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_257/isuhani_136936651528829hV8_JPEG/IMG_1895.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130524_257/isuhani_136936651528829hV8_JPEG/IMG_1895.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_257/isuhani_136936651528829hV8_JPEG/IMG_1895.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">광화문. </span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/908495f44085e943.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130524_5/isuhani_1369366515622HPJbJ_JPEG/IMG_1898.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/908495f44085e943.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>사람 모이는 곳에는 항상 있는 노점 아저씨들. </p>\r\n<p>우리&nbsp;애들은 절대 그냥 지나치지 않아요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_286/isuhani_1369366515801r3HK2_JPEG/IMG_1907.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130524_286/isuhani_1369366515801r3HK2_JPEG/IMG_1907.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_286/isuhani_1369366515801r3HK2_JPEG/IMG_1907.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369366893289\"></span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369366893289\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369366894221\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369366894221\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369366895113\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369366895113\">&#65279;</span> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">광화문을 들어서면 입장권을 받는 곳이 나오는데,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">사람이 너무 많아서 안내요원이 입장권을 일일이 확인하지도 못하더군요. 어찌해야 할지 몰라서 그냥 멍하니 계셨어요. ㅎ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">사람들은 마구마구 앞 사람을 밀어내면서 무조건 들어가고 봅니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">통제가 안되요 -.-;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p></span>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_50/isuhani_136936651600403PUL_JPEG/IMG_1916.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130524_50/isuhani_136936651600403PUL_JPEG/IMG_1916.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_50/isuhani_136936651600403PUL_JPEG/IMG_1916.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그래도.. 경복궁의 야경은 운치가 있더군요. </p>\r\n<p>느긋하게 즐기지 못한다는 건 아쉬워요.</p>\r\n<p>전망 좋은 곳은 뒷사람을 위해 비켜줘야하거든요 ㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/18bb6c72fd15238d.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130524_78/isuhani_13693665162232EdNI_JPEG/IMG_1921.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/18bb6c72fd15238d.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>사람들 왕래하는 곳에서 잠시 앉아서 쉽니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>'그런 표정 짓지 말자구~!'</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f146ef9f922003ff.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130524_138/isuhani_1369366516490uBCr9_JPEG/IMG_1953.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f146ef9f922003ff.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>'그렇지..</p>\r\n<p>지금같은</p>\r\n<p>마를린 먼로 같은 표정이 훨씬 이쁘다!'</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_75/isuhani_1369366516737LKz0r_JPEG/IMG_2011.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130524_75/isuhani_1369366516737LKz0r_JPEG/IMG_2011.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_75/isuhani_1369366516737LKz0r_JPEG/IMG_2011.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>인파로 북적이지만</p>\r\n<p>그래도 조명을 받은 경복궁의 모습은 아름답더군요</p>\r\n<p>근정전 위로 달도 뜨고. 좋아요~</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_213/isuhani_1369366516985D39qE_JPEG/IMG_2028.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130524_213/isuhani_1369366516985D39qE_JPEG/IMG_2028.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_213/isuhani_1369366516985D39qE_JPEG/IMG_2028.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>기다림 끝에. 경회루를 찍습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>내 카메라는</p>\r\n<p>6d 입니다. </p>\r\n<p>iso 감도가 좋아서 밤에 찍어도 환하게 나오는 장점이 있는데</p>\r\n<p>조명이 잘 된 곳을 찍으니.. 너무 밝게 나오는 단점도 있네요</p>\r\n<p>근데</p>\r\n<p>이걸 어떻게 조정하는지 몰라요 ㅜ.ㅠ </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f9190d84ea2b7681.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130524_267/isuhani_1369366547931iMjYE_JPEG/IMG_2031.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f9190d84ea2b7681.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">광화문으로 들어가서</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">근정전을 한바퀴 돌고</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">경회루를 거쳐 숲을지나</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">경복궁역쪽으로 나옵니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">숲속을 거니는 수많은 연인들, 잔디밭에서 쉬고 있는 사람들. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">보기 좋아요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">역시나.. 사람만 좀 더 적었으면 </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">운치만점!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">경복궁역 인근에서 치맥을 하는데</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">자리잡기가 어렵더군요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">어렵사리 자리를 잡고 치킨에 맥주 한잔 하는데</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">애들이 너무 졸려합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">남은 치킨 포장해서 집으로 come back home.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_180/isuhani_1369366517134sLtsH_JPEG/IMG_2041.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130524_180/isuhani_1369366517134sLtsH_JPEG/IMG_2041.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6914E89')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130524_180/isuhani_1369366517134sLtsH_JPEG/IMG_2041.JPG?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>집으로 오는 차 안에서 골아떨어진 아이들</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>남매가.</p>\r\n<p>잠자는 모습도 똑같아요. ㅎㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
